  "title": "refinementList with a sub refinementList",
  "body": "Hello,\r\n\r\nIs it possible to create a new widget that can handle sub refinements lists?\r\n\r\nSo for example we want to show brand + model in 1 refinement list like this:\r\n- Brand 1\r\n   - Model 1\r\n   - Model 2\r\n-Brand 2\r\n   - Model 3\r\n   - Model 4\r\n- Brand 3\r\n   - Model 5\r\netc.\r\n\r\nBrand 1, 2 and 3 is generated by the attribute brand, model 1, 2, 3 etc by the attribute model but shows only the models that are available with the brandname that is listed above the models list.\r\n\r\nIs this already available? ",
